0.4.0
=====

- Get the album cover from the ID3 tag if available [Lee Willis]
- Sort artists like "Cardigans, The" instead of "The Cardigans" [Jorn Baayen]
- Include playlist duration in playlist label when in shuffle mode [Jorn Baayen]
- Reduce memory footprint [Jorn Baayen]
- Reduce startup time [Jorn Baayen]
- Further UI enhancements [Jorn Baayen]
- Code cleanups [Jorn Baayen]
- Various bugfixes [Jorn Baayen, Vaclav Slavik]
- Improved first start window (Disabled for now) [Viet Yen Nguyen]

0.3.2
=====

- Added a repeat mode [Jorn Baayen]
- Use Gnome proxy settings [Jorn Baayen]
- Use Gnome stock icon system whenever possible [Jorn Baayen]
- Various fixes [Jorn Baayen, Lee Willis]

0.3.1.1
=======

- Improve cover image fetching code some more [Jorn Baayen]
- Use a "downloading" image as album cover when relevant [Jorn Baayen]
- Support mono > 0.29 [Jorn Baayen]

0.3.1
=====

- Added FLAC support [Jorn Baayen]
- Improved Amazon cover image fetching code reliability [Lee Willis,
  Jorn Baayen]
- Added replaygain support for MP3 files using the RVA2 tag [Jorn Baayen]
- Added a Dashboard frontend [Lee Willis]
- Interface enhancements [Jorn Baayen]
- Various fixes [Jorn Baayen]

0.3.0
=====

- Automatically fetch missing album cover images from Amazon.com [Lee Willis,
  Jorn Baayen]
- Multimedia key support (as configure by acme) [Jorn Baayen]
- Can now load playlists from the commandline [Jorn Baayen]
- Added an .applications file, so that Nautilus knows about us [Jorn Baayen]
- Bugfixes [Jorn Baayen]
- Tray icon shows playback status [Sergio Rubio, Jorn Baayen]
- Support replay gain for Ogg Vorbis files [Jorn Baayen]
- Support performer tags [Jorn Baayen]
- UI enhancements [Jorn Baayen]
- Check imported folders for changes on startup [Jorn Baayen]

- New translations (partial):
   Spanish [Sergio Rubio]

